I dont know exactly what I want to do in the future but, I have some inspiration. In fact the show I love the most is " How I met your mother". In this show there are a lot of jokes and there is a women. Her name is Alex Dupont. So Alex Dupont is a beautiful and smart women. Who is a reporter. And when i see this show when I'm 10 years old. She really inspire me, and the work seem funny and hard at the same time. So this make me want to be a reporter.
However I'm not in infocom just for that, no actually when I turn 16 yeras old my mother came the Maire of my town. Then she gave me the possibility to take care and make the acount Instagram of my town. Like that the youngest of the town can know what happen, like the activities or the evenment! My mother is also my inspiration and she actually help me to find what I wanna do. Because with that instagram account I realise that I what to do communication again!
Finally, since I'm young I'm attract by the work who are a little bit hard, you know, I want a dangerous job. And we saw on the television, how dangerous the job of a report can be. Or in many shows. Also since I'm young I always love wrote. I remember with my best friend and elementary school we wrote many papers news! By the way he is in infocom too!
